&mo LAYER_Mod  &kp END  &kp PAGE_UP  &kp PAGE_DOWN  &kp HOME  &thumb LAYER_Keypad RETURN  &thumb LAYER_Cursor TAB  &kp BACKSPACE  &thumb LAYER_System RETURN  &kp BACKSPACE  &thumb LAYER_Symbol SPACE  &kp LEFT  &kp DOWN  &kp UP  &kp RIGHT  &mo LAYER_Mod
